skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dad jokes
des:
Ask for Dad Jokes, and start laughing with some funny, or maybe not so funny, dad jokes.
Dad Jokes provides fun the whole family can enjoy, especially dads...

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Dad jokes" or "Alexa, open Dad jokes".
To get a get dad joke, just say "tell me a dad joke" and say: "next" to get a new one.
At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
